name: Nanobots Eat the Sky
description:
Random walker nanobots both breed and paint over a generated background of an evening sky.

As each new nanobot is born, they are assigned a random color from a set of colours: red, yellow, green, blue, white or black.

The nanobots will eventually fill the entire sky although this will take a significant amount of time. They tend to swarm around the center of the canvas and they will stop breeding once their population reaches a maximum (this maximum is relative to the size of the canvas).
